{
  "texts": [
    "The tests reported in the previous section reveal that CNNs trained on virtual PDFs perform better than those trained on XRD patterns when dealing with single-phase samples.",
    "To clarify why this might be, we inspect the Class Activation Map (CAM) of each model.",
    "The CAM illustrates which parts of the input spectrum most significantly contribute to the model's output 4, 21.",
    "Taking TiO 2 as an example, we examine the CAM for each model using its associated input.",
    "The XRD pattern and virtual PDF for this sample, as well as their respective CAMs, are shown in Fig. 3."
  ]
}